  "excerpt": "<p><p>My Etsy Picks: Football Season I may not be a giant sports fan- football is something I watch once a year, during Super Bowl, for the commercials- but I can certainly appreciate the energy surrounding it! Football fans are passionate about their teams, and live on the edges of their seats, whilst shouting (a lot), […]</p></p>",
  "content": "<p>My Etsy Picks: Football Season</p><p>I may not be a giant sports fan- football is something I watch once a year, during Super Bowl, for the commercials- but I can certainly appreciate the energy surrounding it! Football fans are passionate about their teams, and live on the edges of their seats, whilst shouting (a lot), during each and every game. They’re also always decked out in their team’s colors and logos- which is definitely something I can get behind! I’ve seen tons of amazing football themed products on Etsy before, so I thought I’d go through them and put them all in one place for you!</p><p>Each of these Etsy artisans have created awesome football or team themed items that you will love! Click each of their links below to check them out and give them some love! Check out the</p><a title=\"Football Season! Treasury by Katie Crafts on Etsy\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/treasury/MTAzNjM3NjF8MjcyNDIwMTc2NQ/its-football-season\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong><em><p>full treasury right here!</p></em></strong></a><ol><li><a title=\"Functional Sculpture on Etsy\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/96756450/new-york-giants-3d-wall-art-metal-emblem?ref=sr_gallery_33&#x26;ga_search_query=football+giants&#x26;ga_page=2&#x26;ga_search_type=all&#x26;ga_view_type=gallery\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Functional Sculpture</a></li><li><a title=\"Kountry Kreations on Etsy\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/78679544/crochet-baby-football-hat-newborn?ref=sr_gallery_2&#x26;ga_search_query=football+hat&#x26;ga_ref=auto1&#x26;ga_search_type=all&#x26;ga_view_type=gallery\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Kountry Kreations</a></li><li><a title=\"Mural Max on Etsy\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/129266648/football-canvas-art-sports-nursery?ref=shop_home_active_18\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Mural Max</a></li><li><a title=\"Appalachian Primitive on Etsy\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/104829272/we-interrupt-this-marriage-for-football?ref=sr_gallery_2&#x26;ga_search_query=football&#x26;ga_search_type=all&#x26;ga_view_type=gallery\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Appalachian Primitive</a></li><li><a title=\"The Craftin Bear on Etsy\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/200142377/pittsburgh-steelers-burlap-wreath-w?ref=sr_gallery_23&#x26;ga_search_query=football+steelers&#x26;ga_search_type=all&#x26;ga_view_type=gallery\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">The Craftin Bear</a></li><li><a title=\"Crazy Fun Nail Art on Etsy\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/200633731/philadelphia-eagles-nfl-football-nail?ref=sr_gallery_14&#x26;ga_search_query=football+eagles&#x26;ga_order=most_relevant&#x26;ga_search_type=all&#x26;ga_view_type=gallery\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Crazy Fun Nail Art</a></li><li><a title=\"Love Inked on Etsy\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/198809282/football-season-tshirt-new-orleans?ref=sr_gallery_27&#x26;ga_search_query=football+shirt+-child&#x26;ga_order=most_relevant&#x26;ga_page=2&#x26;ga_search_type=all&#x26;ga_view_type=gallery\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Love Inked</a></li><li><a title=\"Mik Mak Bowtique on Etsy\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/200658000/i-watch-espn-with-my-daddy-giants-ny?ref=sr_gallery_14&#x26;ga_search_query=football+giants&#x26;ga_page=2&#x26;ga_search_type=all&#x26;ga_view_type=gallery\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Mik Mak Bowtique</a></li><li><a title=\"Riverstone Goods on Etsy\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/200395045/we-match-the-couple-that-watches?ref=sc_1&#x26;sref=sr_1c82944dcf31858a6b3e9cb86530bf5dfa17ff1c7985c1fe2d1bc188de3d0d4c_1410188856_15013193_tote&#x26;sref2=MjAwMzk1MDQ1%3AdG90ZQ..%3AMTUwMTMxOTM.%3AZm9vdGJhbGwgdG90ZQ..%3Ady4w%3AMTQxMDE4ODg1Ng..%3AMzoxNDEwMTg4ODU2OlFKZUN2YTZfblJvOF9RMTg3Z0tYU0JSU2F0Yms6MjRkOWU5NmYzYzZlNWIzMmYxYzRlNzU1ZGI3M2ZkY2UxMjAwYTIxMWNiOTRjZWYwOTQ1MTgyODAxMjB